<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王用了很长时间，终于到了海的另一边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来到了一片新土地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走了很多年，去了很多地方，见了很多人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29230</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他没有找到圣人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最终，他来到了一座山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走在山路上时，听到了砍木头的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个樵夫正在砍柴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！”美猴王说，“这座山中有圣人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>樵夫吓得斧子掉在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是……猴子？”他说，“你居然会说话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我会说话。”美猴王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想长生不老。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道我去哪里可以找到圣人吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>樵夫抓了抓脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我知道的。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这山上有位名叫菩提祖师的圣人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常有智慧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去哪里可以找到他？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只要沿着这条小路一直走，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就可以到达他的住所了。”樵夫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢！”美猴王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥手告别了樵夫，沿着小路一直跑过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他就看到了山边的一座庙宇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这座庙的大厅里，菩提祖师正和他的弟子们坐在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着自己的大弟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去开门吧。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有个新弟子就要来了。让他进来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个弟子表情困惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“遵命，师父。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个弟子起来走到庙门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向门外看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！”美猴王大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来见菩提祖师的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，美猴王就站在了菩提祖师面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想成为你的弟子。”美猴王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只不过是一只猴子。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么能做我的弟子？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我确实是只猴子，但我能说会走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我还会做很多其他的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我差不多用了 13 年的时间才来到这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我很确定我有资格做你的弟子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师看了美猴王一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的父母是谁？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美猴王挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有父母。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是石头里出来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有意思。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可能是天地造出来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以做我的弟子，但你需要一个名字。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他思考了一会：“我就叫你孙悟空吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在之后的七年里，孙悟空一直住在庙里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这只猴子每天冥想、听他的师父讲课，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还要做一些杂活儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，菩提祖师正在授课，悟空突然开始跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么敢在我授课的时候跳舞？”他大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我实在是太开心了，所以我要跳舞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师平静下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很开心？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，”孙悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跟着您学习，我很高兴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你来我这里已经很久了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你想跟我学习什么呢？”菩提祖师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请您告诉我，我应该学习什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以教你预知未来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你喜欢学这个吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能吧。”悟空说，“这会让我长生不老吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然不能。”菩提祖师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就算了。”悟空说，”教我点别的吧！“</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”菩提祖师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那么学点神奇的呼吸之术怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它能让我长生不老吗？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不能。”菩提祖师皱着眉头说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我没兴趣。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菩提祖师生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>359320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他站起身来在悟空的脑袋上敲了三下，然后离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>359321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，”另一个弟子说，“你对师父太无礼了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>365865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>369674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他学生也这么想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>369675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空却笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>374885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他弟子都不明白。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>374886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚刚菩提祖师是给了悟空一个暗示。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>